channel.title: Drizzles - Jelmø [Project, Collab?]
channel.description:
This project is already done. Do you want to hear the result? Go to https://soundcloud.com/jelmo_music/drizzles.
If you’re still interested in a collab, feel free to send me a message!
___
Hi! I’m Jelmø. I’ve been posting tracks for a while but never did a collab. However, I really want to make something together with someone.
So, let’s collab!
https://soundcloud.com/jelmo_music/drizzles-1/s-whewF
Here’s a link to a project I started. If you would like to work on this with me. Just PM me and I’ll send you the project link. I’m looking forward to work with someone!
~Jelmø
[details="PS."] I also want to release the track on Spotify, Apple Music and Shazam. So it’ll be cool if you have already released to these stores. [/details]
